      "source": [
        "## Creating arrays\n",
        "\n",
        "### Arrays created from lists and other array-like objects\n"
      ],
      "id": "78d40bf5"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.array([1, 2, 3, 4])\n",
        "data.ndim, data.shape"
      ],
      "id": "e8e7939c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.array(((1, 2), (3, 4)))\n",
        "data.ndim, data.shape"
      ],
      "id": "57fffc35",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Arrays filled with constant values\n"
      ],
      "id": "4280961a"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.zeros((2, 3))"
      ],
      "id": "916b55ba",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.ones(4)\n",
        "data, data.dtype"
      ],
      "id": "5065dd2f",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "5.4 * np.ones(10)"
      ],
      "id": "3995cb05",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.full(10, 5.4) # slightly more efficient"
      ],
      "id": "af4143a8",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "x1 = np.empty(5)\n",
        "x1.fill(3.0)\n",
        "x1"
      ],
      "id": "ef432dca",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Arrays filled with incremental sequences\n"
      ],
      "id": "80fbd828"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.arange(0, 11, 1)"
      ],
      "id": "84b680e0",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.linspace(0, 10, 11)  # generally recommended"
      ],
      "id": "72ea7975",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Arrays filled with logarithmic sequences\n"
      ],
      "id": "4cb19bf3"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.logspace(0, 2, 10)  # 5 data points between 10**0=1 to 10**2=100"
      ],
      "id": "31faa4e6",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Mesh grid arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "7c62759f"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "x = np.array([-1, 0, 1])\n",
        "y = np.array([-2, 0, 2])\n",
        "\n",
        "X, Y = np.meshgrid(x, y)"
      ],
      "id": "65a63391",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "X"
      ],
      "id": "956f525c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Y"
      ],
      "id": "8ab548f4",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Z = (X + Y)**2\n",
        "Z"
      ],
      "id": "74db3575",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Creating uninitialized arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "f58bd946"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.empty(3, dtype=float)"
      ],
      "id": "56f52460",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Creating arrays with properties of other arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "f3528962"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "def f(x):    \n",
        "    y = np.ones_like(x)    # compute with x and y    \n",
        "    return y\n",
        "\n",
        "x = np.array([[1, 2, 3], [4, 5, 6]])\n",
        "y = f(x)\n",
        "y"
      ],
      "id": "b83cffe5",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Creating matrix arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "95f07ac3"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.identity(4)"
      ],
      "id": "fabacd81",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.eye(4, k=1)"
      ],
      "id": "0884e7a4",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.eye(4, k=-1)"
      ],
      "id": "b5c209e1",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.diag(np.arange(0, 20, 5))"
      ],
      "id": "99385efe",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Indexing and slicing\n",
        "\n",
        "### One-dimensional arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "39786c13"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a = np.arange(0, 11)\n",
        "a"
      ],
      "id": "f7883e8a",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[0]"
      ],
      "id": "97ad5b12",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[-1]"
      ],
      "id": "35a861e7",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[4]"
      ],
      "id": "359214ae",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "8473f018"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[1:-1]"
      ],
      "id": "c364fc8d",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[1:-1:2]"
      ],
      "id": "9fc1d130",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "5a822053"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[:5]"
      ],
      "id": "561eb97d",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[-5:]"
      ],
      "id": "4a43ceee",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[::-2]"
      ],
      "id": "895a1ebb",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Multidimensional arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "d3128cc3"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "f = lambda m, n: n + 10*m"
      ],
      "id": "f43e5cd2",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "# please search for numpy.fromfunction at google\n",
        "A = np.fromfunction(f, (6, 6), dtype=int)\n",
        "A  "
      ],
      "id": "a5f536bf",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[:, 1]  # the second column"
      ],
      "id": "7273316a",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[1, :]  # the second row"
      ],
      "id": "03ff1b11",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[:3, :3]"
      ],
      "id": "b0962359",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[3:, :3]"
      ],
      "id": "ae094aeb",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[::2, ::2]"
      ],
      "id": "7cae09fc",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[1::2, 1::3]"
      ],
      "id": "0ad18a58",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Views\n",
        "\n",
        "* Subarrays that are extracted from arrays using slice operations are **alternative views** of the same underlying array data. That is, $~$they are arrays that refer to the same data in memory as the original array, $~$but with a different `strides` configuration\n",
        "\n",
        "* When elements in a view are assigned new values, $~$the values of the original\n",
        "array are therefore also updated. For example,\n"
      ],
      "id": "9a510734"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B = A[1:5, 1:5]\n",
        "B"
      ],
      "id": "5bea9c54",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B[:, :] = 0\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "eeacbe76",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "* When a copy rather than a view is needed, the view can be copied explicitly by using the `copy` method of the `ndarray` instance\n"
      ],
      "id": "86ca86eb"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "C = B[1:3, 1:3].copy()\n",
        "C"
      ],
      "id": "14e709a7",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "C[:, :] = 1\n",
        "C"
      ],
      "id": "2e857dcf",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B"
      ],
      "id": "576ab236",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Fancy indexing and boolean-valued indexing\n"
      ],
      "id": "fbd0bb1b"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.linspace(0, 1, 11)\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "0f866fb3",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[np.array([0, 2, 4])]"
      ],
      "id": "ef05fd8d",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[[0, 2, 4]]"
      ],
      "id": "81828f44",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "7bcc362d"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A > 0.5"
      ],
      "id": "743996ef",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[A > 0.5]"
      ],
      "id": "78c3fece",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "* Unlike arrays created by using slices, $~$**the arrays returned using fancy indexing and Boolean-valued\n",
        "indexing are not views**, $~$but rather new independent arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "0b54d80c"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.arange(10)\n",
        "indices = [2, 4, 6]"
      ],
      "id": "2dc0e788",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B = A[indices]"
      ],
      "id": "91067385",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B[0] = -1\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "b26e43bd",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[indices] = -1\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "a81a7415",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "237fe704"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.arange(10)"
      ],
      "id": "78ca0e20",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B = A[A > 5]"
      ],
      "id": "f066ac25",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B[0] = -1\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "38eae4b3",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[A > 5] = -1\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "ff741048",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Summery\n"
      ],
      "id": "15e7f1d8"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), ':, :')"
      ],
      "id": "fff47d45",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '0')"
      ],
      "id": "4f6e9eb1",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '1, :')"
      ],
      "id": "52edce19",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), ':, 2')"
      ],
      "id": "d051aa14",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "80c88cee"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '0:2, 0:2')"
      ],
      "id": "7d52cd47",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '0:2, 2:4')"
      ],
      "id": "d0a05096",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '::2, ::2')"
      ],
      "id": "1944a69c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '1::2, 1::2')"
      ],
      "id": "1d5b2e7c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), ':, [0, 3]')"
      ],
      "id": "22aed21b",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '[1, 3], [0, 3]')"
      ],
      "id": "77313e62",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), ':, [False, True, True, False]')"
      ],
      "id": "c9a0ec49",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '1:3, [False, True, True, False]')"
      ],
      "id": "4c5297aa",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Reshaping and resizing\n",
        "\n",
        "* Reshaping an array does not require modifying the underlying array data; it only changes in how the data is interpreted, by redefining the array’s strides attribute\n"
      ],
      "id": "fed26400"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.array([[1, 2], [3, 4]])\n",
        "data1 = np.reshape(data, (1, 4))\n",
        "data1"
      ],
      "id": "40b8c4c7",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data1[0, 1] = -1\n",
        "data"
      ],
      "id": "006b69d6",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data2 = data.reshape(4)\n",
        "data2"
      ],
      "id": "a9d39c58",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data2[1] = -2\n",
        "data"
      ],
      "id": "714c6e2c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "c75d96b4"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.array([[1, 2], [3, 4]])\n",
        "data1 = np.ravel(data)\n",
        "data1"
      ],
      "id": "f6459540",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data1[0] = -1\n",
        "data"
      ],
      "id": "5cebae8e",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "* The `ndarray` method `flatten` perform the same function, $~$but\n",
        "returns a **copy** instead of a view\n"
      ],
      "id": "3a700736"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data2 = data.flatten()\n",
        "data2"
      ],
      "id": "9e8dc945",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data2[0] = -2\n",
        "data"
      ],
      "id": "89e344d7",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "4073ae26"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.arange(0, 5)\n",
        "data.shape"
      ],
      "id": "d6564d25",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "column = data[:, np.newaxis]\n",
        "column"
      ],
      "id": "f2d4c762",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "column.shape"
      ],
      "id": "e075d08c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "row = data[np.newaxis, :]\n",
        "row"
      ],
      "id": "d3b93c2a",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "row.shape"
      ],
      "id": "1132e613",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "row[0, 0] = -1\n",
        "data"
      ],
      "id": "60a47dce",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
